{
  "texts": [
    "And the Lord saw their repentance, and he relented from the calamity that he had intended to bring upon them.",
    "And Jonah was glad.",
    "He was glad that the people of Nineveh had repented of their sins.",
    "He was glad that the Lord had spared them.",
    "And he was glad that he had been a part of God's plan to save the people of Nineveh."
  ]
}